<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM11.6">
<l>kaipporuḷkaṇ muṉṉamē kaikkoṇṭār kāvirinīr</l>
<l>ceyppuraḷa vōṭun tiruvaraṅkac celvaṉār</l>
<l>epporuṭkum niṉṟārkku meytātu nāṉmaṟaiyiṉ</l>
<l>coṟporuḷāy niṉṟāreṉ meypporuḷuṅ koṇṭārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The Wealthy Man from Śrīraṅgam</l>
<l rend="indent">—where the water from the Kāverī runs in such a way that the fields overflow—</l>
<l>remains in all objects [but] is not reachable by anyone,</l>
<l>He who remains as the meanings of the words of the four Vedas</l>
<l>Previously seized the objects from [our] hands;</l>
<l rend="indent">[now] He has also taken the object that is my body!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
